column3: Add missing immutable field methods. Add tests
Implement possibility to add custom builder factories
Add possibility to define local builder factories for a single loading procedure
Add support for multiple resourceBundles in FluentViewLoader #518

[#543] Incorrect exception message in ViewLoaderReflectionUtils

Signed-off-by: Nils Christian Ehmke <nils@rhocas.de>

Fix for #547 remove static dependency to PostConstruct annotation

This way it's now easier to use the library with Java 9 and upwards as in Java 9 the annotation `@PostConstruct` isn't available anymore by default.
Enables to change configurations via maven-profile.
